Class MusicPanel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container

            • ng.co.ovo.Multimedia.MusicPanel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class MusicPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Author:
    ovokerie creates the panel that reads music files and the associated icons. The icons are represented by labels and their listeners are added and implemented. This panel is displayed on the main frame when it is created The external library used is the VLCJ library which is open source.
